Ako nemate pitanja,
pozdravite se, povucite se.

286
00:22:17,878 --> 00:22:20,381
Na moj signal počinje borba.

287
00:22:26,971 --> 00:22:29,769
Jesi spreman? Spreman?

288
00:22:29,932 --> 00:22:31,024
Počnite!

289
