290
00:22:53,664 --> 00:22:55,086
Mora da pazi na tu nogu.

291
00:23:12,308 --> 00:23:13,309
Hajde, Majk!

292
00:23:23,694 --> 00:23:25,822
Ne dozvoli mu da ti to radi, Majk!

293
